    "body_html": null,
    "truncated_body_text": "As you know, I don’t do short-term speculative trades with Bitcoin. The main reason is that its fundamentals are not well defined yet, and its trend is much slower than that of the stock market. This may sound strange given the difference in their volatilities, but if you watch BTC, what it mostly does is one big, sharp move toward a target, followed by a multi-week range-bound consolidation there.",
